summary: Tired of marry the same Ysolda again and again? Try a blonde Ysolda, just to change a little bit.
descriptionHtml:
[font=Arial][color=blue][i]I really thank you for the support, for the downloads, the endorsements, the pm\'s, and the comments. Its important to me to know that you like this little mod, and I wanna thank you![/i]

[size=18][u]Thank you for the 50 downloads![/u][/color][/font][/size]
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Hi all, this is my first mod. First of all, thanks for reading.

[i][color=olive]Well, I just get the idea to modify Ysolda for myself; to make a little change vanilla-friendly. I know that its not big deal; not like other mods, but I just want to share it.[/color][/i]

[b]Its [u]just a skin-change[/u][/b], nothing else. Anyways, you have free way to mod it if you want.

Im using the [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2812]Better Females by Bella[/url] mod, but [b]this is [u]just a vanilla change[/b][/u]. If you have got another texture\'s for woman (or if you just have the vanilla version), [u]its [b]NOT[/b] a problem[/u]. Probabbly you should get a less smooth skin, but the face change should be there. Anyways, I really recommend the mod.


[i]If you like it, you may try my other vanilla changes:[/i]

[b]Dravynea the Stoneweaver[/b]: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24694]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24694[/url]

[b]Avrusa Sarethi[/b]: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24500]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24500[/url]

[b]Borgakh the Steel Heart[/b]: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24418]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24418[/url]

[b]Brelyna Maryon[/b]: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24435]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24435[/url]

[b]Lydia[/b]: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24661]http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/24661[/url]

Hope you enjoy it! 

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[u][i][b][size=14]New version![/u][/i][/b][/size]

[i]Its not big deal, but [b]I just tweek her jaw a little bit[/b] to make it more curve and thin. The vanilla one (in the pictures) its good, but I think that this suits better for her. Give it a try! And [u]thank you for downloads[/u]![/i]
author: ArouetX
